%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Usuari
    participant Client as Client MCP<br/>(Claude Desktop)
    participant App as Next.js<br/>frontend
    participant Auth as Supabase Auth
    participant API as /api/mcp<br/>route handler
    participant Lib as createMcpSupabase<br/>Client (auth.ts)
    participant Server as createMcpServer<br/>(server.ts)
    participant DB as Supabase Postgres<br/>(RLS-gated)

    User->>App: Login OAuth (Google/GitHub)
    App->>Auth: redirect to OAuth provider
    Auth-->>App: callback amb code
    App->>Auth: exchange code for JWT
    Auth-->>App: access_token (JWT)
    Note over User,App: Sergi configura Claude Desktop<br/>amb el JWT com a Bearer token

    User->>Client: invoca eina MCP<br/>(p.ex. search_notes "lidl")
    Client->>API: POST /api/mcp<br/>Authorization: Bearer <jwt><br/>JSON-RPC 2.0
    API->>Lib: createMcpSupabaseClient(req)
    Lib->>Lib: extractBearerToken(req)
    Lib->>Auth: supabase.auth.getUser(token)
    Auth-->>Lib: { user }
    Lib->>Lib: createServerClient amb<br/>global.headers.Authorization
    Lib-->>API: { client, user }
    API->>Server: createMcpServer(client)
    Server-->>API: McpServer amb tools registrades
    API->>Server: server.connect(transport)
    Server->>Server: dispatch tool: searchByEmbedding
    Server->>DB: rpc match_notes(embedding, 0.1, 5)
    Note over DB: RLS aplica<br/>auth.uid() = user_id
    DB-->>Server: top-5 notes del user
    Server-->>API: content blocks
    API-->>Client: JSON-RPC response
    Client-->>User: render dels resultats
